### Get all users (JSON API)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Render login page (HTML)
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Accept: text/html

###

### Register a new user (adjust the form fields to match your app)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=youruser&password=yourpass

###

### Login with a user (adjust the form fields to match your app)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=youruser&password=yourpass

###